name: slip through your fingertips
description: I relate to this feeling so much now. You know when i started drawing this the baby was okay and the mother was enjoying her hot bath. But as time passed the baby started melting more and more... what would you do if you were the mother? Nothing. All you could do was to witness your child slip through your hands. And now that i finished the drawing the time has stopped. The mother is screaming eternally. And watching her baby in that shape.
